text:
Ah, there you are. Rinze,
I have some documents I'd like you to take a look at.

Yes, it's for HO-KA-GO CLIMAX GIRLS――
in other words, the costumes Rinze and the others will wear.
So, Rinze's is the blue one, right?

Yes. We've asked the designer to make it
tailored to suit Rinze.

......Fufu...
I'm looking forward... to the day when I get to wear it...
